# Import paths

`@/` in `src/`, `@tooling/` in tooling; same-folder `./` only; **never `../`**; `.js` ESM specifiers that resolve to `.ts` on disk. Enforced by `src/tests/global/import-paths.global.test.ts`. Detail: CLAUDE.md › Import paths.
